{
  "stem": "21786.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Just before we left, a little vignette.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I'm standing there with Eva in this loft, and we already have got some kind of a small suitcase with us, and a rucksack.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I said to her, you have got this ring, which was strictly forbidden, naturally, with a relatively big diamond.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You'll never carry it through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It might cause your destruction.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Give me the thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I kneeled down, and I put-- as I build the floor, so it was on 2x2s-- and I went in between as far as I could go, and on a s-- flat piece of wood, I placed the ring under the floorboard.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We all went into the same wagon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There have been wagons.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "One can see it in the Holocaust Museum in Washington.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was originally for eight horses or 40 soldiers, or in this case, about 150 or 200 Jews, packed together like sardines.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We took off, and we went all through the day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We knew that we are passing through Prague, for one could see through a small window things, and we passed through northern Bohemia.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And finally, in the morning, early in the morning-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] no, it was at night, sorry.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stopped and we were-- the person who was at this little window with barbed wire on it, there was standing a-- a-- a railway-- a railway man at the platform of a station with a little light there.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were hearing, where are we?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said to us in Polish, you?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You are in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he did this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in that moment, the doors opened.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
